\id 3JN - South Tairora (Omwunra Toqura) NT -Papua New Guinea 2001 (DBL 2014)
\h 3 Ioni
\toc1 Ioniva ekyaara qara vara kyora
\toc2 3 Ioni
\toc3 3Ion
\mt1 3 IONI
\mt2 Ioniva ekyaara qara vara kyora
\ip Iesusira qati vara sivuma kyovaro nyaamwuni uro varuvaro airi ihi 60 ihive nritarovaro Ioniva mwaa quara qara ntumwa tora. Vaisi mpovanto Kaiasiva varuvaro Ioniva mwianra kyuqema kyera Iesusira nraaqiaravanto nyianrasaita nrumu varihuaqa ntaqikyiqira quante timwa kyero vaisi mpo Ntiotarepirara uaqia hi kyaiqara uti variho timwa kyero Ntemitiriaasirara kyuqe kyaiqa vare variho timwa kyero qara ntumwa tora.
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Kaiasio, nte Ioniva Kotira nraaqiaraqaa ntaqikyi varuvama mwaa quara ini qara ntumwa tena. Po, Kaiasio, qutaaqama kyeroma ni mutukyavanto iara vahiro.
\v 2 Ni katao, e hia nriqa quani inraikyara varairaro i mwamwantavanto kyuqema kyero vahiarive tina, nte iara rieqanama Kotirara aakyara nte varura. Nte ntapihi kyauqaro i vu nraato mwutukyavanto Kotirara kyuqema kyero vaihara variananra.
\p 
\v 3 Tiri tiqata vakyaa mponramwuvanto e hiananrasaita mwaini nri nteta iara mwiva kyuqema kyero qutaa qua tutero variqiro vi variho qiavana nte mwi quara riena qamwateqana varuqo. Qio nte i ntapihi kyauqara e Kotira qua qutaa qua nraahu riemwaqira vi variaravama variaro.
\p 
\v 4 Qikye, nte qaiqaa nanra qua mpo rienave nte qamwataaninra. Ni nraaqiarara mwihua qutaa qua nraahu riemwaqita vi variavo ti vari quara, mwi quara rieqanama nte nronraqama kyena qamwataaninra.
\s1 Ioniva Kaiasirara kyuqe kyaiqa vare variaro tura
\p 
\v 5 Ni vaisio, e tiri tiqata vakyaa kyaahaqama nyateqarama hia viri taqaarahuavata kyaahaqama nyateqarama kyuqema kyera kyaiqa vare varira.
\p 
\v 6 I mwutukyavanto mwihuara vahira mwihua tiri timwa timwiavata tire Iesusira nraakye qora mwaini varurahua riaunanra. Mwi vaisihua Kotira kyaiqa vare varirara tira, e mwihua kyuqema kyera kyaraqotairave, mpo inraikyaqotairave, kyaahaqama nyatairata aanraqaa quata.
\p 
\v 7 Hia Iesusira qua riaa nraakye qorahua variavata mwihua hia mwihuara munima timwivaqeta aanraqaa tuvare quare tiraitita, mwihua Iesusi Karaisira nrutuara rieqata mpo mwatukya mpo mwatukya nrohiqata Karaisira qua timwa nyi variara.
\p 
\v 8 Mwihua mwitaamaqita vi variarara tita, tire mwihuara qamwateqata sita kyeta vateta kyaahaqama nyataaravama vahiro. Tire mwihua kyaahaqamaqita viqata mwihuavata tirevata kuaa kyaiqa mwia vare variararo qutaa quavanto qioma viro nrinro hiananro.
\s1 Ioniva Ntiotarepisiva uaqia hi kyaiqara utiho tura
\p 
\v 9 Nkye Iesusira nraakye qora mwini variahua, nte nkyini qara vara kyauqaro Ntiotarepisiva kyaakueqama kyero hia tiri qua riarero uti variro. Mwi vaisiva nronra vaisiqama viro mpohuaqaa ntaqikyianinranra nraahuma mwia mwutukya vaiharo variro.
\p 
\v 10 Nraakiara nkye hinani uro ntena nte mwia uaqia hi kyaiqara qovarama kyarera. Mwiva tiri nrutuvanto mwatani tumi quarive tiro, unra qua tiriara ti variho. Hia mwi qiara nraahuve. Mwiva varihata tiri qata vakyaahua mpo mwatukya mpo mwatukyani nrohi variahua nriavaro mwiva kepukyaqama kyero hia nte mwihua qamwata nyatarerave timwa kyero taqaiharo mpovanto mwihuara qamwatero sita kyero nai nraamwuqi vatarero utiharo mwiva mwiavata vu nraato nrenro tiqaro, E mwihua sita vatairera, mwia kyaara i raaquta kyaarara hia tirivata variqara Kotira qua rienanrave, tiro. Mwiva mwitaa tiqaro mpohuavata antuare varira.
\s1 Ntemitiriaasira kyuqe kyaiqara tura
\p 
\v 11 Ni vaisio, hia uaqia hi kyaiqara utihua vi aanranraqaa quante. Kyuqe kyaiqa nraahu vare aanranra mwiaqaa nraahu quante. Kyuqe kyaiqa nraahu vare variva, mwiva Kotira nraaqiarama variho. Uaqia hi kyaiqara uti vari vaisiva hia Kotira okyara taqaivama.
\p 
\v 12 Vaisi mpovanto Ntemitiriaasiva varihata ekyaa nraakye qora mwi vaisirara kyuqe vaisive ti variara. Mwihua taqaavaro mwi vaisiva qutaaqama kyero Kotira kyaiqa vare varira. Tirevata mwi vaisirara kyuqe vaisive turo. Tire mwitaa tunanra evata riaararo qutaa qua nraahuma vahiro.
\s1 Ekyaara qua mwanteqaro tura
\p 
\v 13 Nte airi qua i timwa mwianriva vaihanavata nte hia qaraqitaina i timwa mwinrenra.
\v 14 Nte pataqia vari kyena nte uro i viri taqeqana ivata qua tirera.
\p 
\v 15 Kotiva i kyaahaqama mwatairaro i mwutukyavanto qihaakyama vahirara variante.
\p I qata vakyaa mwaini variahua i qua mwantaavo. Ni kata pakyaa mwini variahua nianra mwiva nkyi qua mwantaiho tira timwa nyiante. 
